---
---
<section class="quote" aria-label="Alpha testimonial">
  <div class="quote-inner">
    <span class="quote-eyebrow">Alpha programme</span>
    <svg class="quote-mark" viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M14 30c0-7 5-12 12-13l1 4c-5 1-8 4-8 9h5v10H10V30h4Zm22 0c0-7 5-12 12-13l1 4c-5 1-8 4-8 9h5v10H32V30h4Z" transform="translate(-4 -4)" fill="currentColor" />
    </svg>
    <blockquote class="quote-body">
      Brackstone gives our team a clearer picture of which enquiries need attention first.
      It keeps follow-ups organised, helps us respond calmly, and means fewer important
      calls get lost during busy clinic days.
    </blockquote>
    <figcaption class="quote-attr">
      <span class="attr-avatar" aria-hidden="true">AL</span>
      <span class="attr-text">
        <strong>Alpha Laser Clinic team</strong>
        <span>Alpha testing partner</span>
      </span>
    </figcaption>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @reference "../../styles/global.css";

  .quote {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-brand-line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-brand-line);
  }

  .quote-inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-brand-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    color: rgba(110, 72, 240, 0.18);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .quote-body {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.4vw, 1.7rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    color: var(--color-brand-ink);
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    quotes: "\201C" "\201D";
  }

  .quote-body::before { content: open-quote; }
  .quote-body::after  { content: close-quote; }

  .quote-attr {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .attr-avatar {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-brand-primary), var(--color-brand-accent));
    color: #fff;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .attr-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .attr-text strong {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-brand-ink);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .attr-text span {
    color: var(--color-brand-muted);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .quote { padding: 3.5rem 1.1rem; }
  }
</style>
